{"tid":2489140,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"「娛賓」女記者中椒休克 警長徐啟迪: 別無選擇下使用最低武力","createTime":"2021-04-14T18:13:18.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-15T00:59:24.000Z","uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"2edd80c1428d51711a5dbc9ef9d72aebf994f3ad","tid":2489140,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T18:13:18.000Z","msg":"網媒「娛賓」女記者去年母親節深夜採訪期間在公園公廁疑遭防暴警施用暴力，包括跪頸及以胡椒噴霧「噴完一支又一支」，女記者一度休克及失禁，最終反被控抗拒警員執行職務罪，案件昨續審。警長稱女記者案發時推女警，屬頑強抵抗，且又撼頭自殘，在別無選擇下使用最低武力，兩度向女記者噴胡椒噴霧，並否認對女記者用不合理及不恰當武力。<br />\n<br />\n案件由主任裁判官嚴舜儀審理，警長58604徐啟迪供稱去年5月11日，被告在旺角洗衣街花園公廁的女廁內推女警，且身體向前踏，作勢逃跑，想衝向公廁門口；又無視警方警告，故依警例使用最低武力噴胡椒噴霧；並指若改用雙手制服被告，有機會令被告或警員受傷。他又指，被告被按在地時曾以頭撼地面，出現自殘行為，且不斷掙扎，他才再次向被告噴胡椒噴霧。<br />\n<br />\n辯方質疑警方濫用權力，對被告使用不恰當及不合理武力，被告「中椒」後休克；又指警長及同袍知悉自己闖禍，事後到醫院查探被告。徐統統否認。<br />\n<br />\n警察公共關係科傳媒聯絡隊高級督察許育芙事後到場，警方從被告背囊找到「娛賓」工作證，但找不到記協發出的證件，她在此前未聽過「娛賓」這網媒名稱，不能確認或否定被告的記者身份。聆訊今續。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210415/PNLU4HL3VBCNVDPW37HYIHB2WU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210415%2FPNLU4HL3VBCNVDPW37HYIHB2WU%2F&d=RjdfG9uxtkM%2FelS3aO62sDyMEfxyOVmMxalVp7jK43I%3D&h=114c9f25\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210415%2FPNLU4HL3VBCNVDPW37HYIHB2WU%2F&h=8f2daabc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210415/PNLU4HL3VBCNVDPW37HYIHB2WU/</a>"},{"pid":"df474947c17026383bbbf5c2eb0516476c1983df","tid":2489140,"uid":51752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T00:06:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"452d48787c35e60b216054fd8460cff85e78c435","tid":2489140,"uid":19640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T00:20:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3fe874e5e3301cc74f160bcd05ffe15fe020edf0","tid":2489140,"uid":237425,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T00:24:36.000Z","msg":"講到咁無奈？<br />\n不如講下女狗做咩入女廁打市民？<br />\n女廁構成暴動定非法集結？<br />\n<br />\n再講咪撚人地係唔係記者<br />\n普通一個市民就可以任你地打到失禁？"},{"pid":"a0baa01644fba3bb88b9949b487a38418d32b3e1","tid":2489140,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T00:41:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0454b75c262a6b8ba22e222fdb9a8d15879e5c5","tid":2489140,"uid":70786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T00:45:22.000Z","msg":"有冇去過醫院探冇紀錄嘅咩？<br />\n一check就知邊個講大話啦"},{"pid":"fd590e59405ff333bab5309d02f56899230263d5","tid":2489140,"uid":207247,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T00:47:58.000Z","msg":"但找不到記協發出的證件 <br />\n要發出d 咩證件先可以採訪？"},{"pid":"5bde29f9f2637167a6bd365382ab538833d23b74","tid":2489140,"uid":39710,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T00:59:24.000Z","msg":"虐打成癮"}]}